{"tid":2297841,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[新TG谷]係死之前 要盡可能吹多啲水","createTime":"2020-11-23T14:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T07:23:02.000Z","uid":128483,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c985830187fbce7c9a38dd9c782bc956bc5037de","tid":2297841,"uid":128483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T14:48:37.000Z","msg":"新TG谷歡迎大家！！！<br />\n我地個谷係希望大家得閒吹下水<br />\n盡可能係死之前放多啲廢野俾呢個社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩開心有趣事就分享 大家一齊笑下<br />\n有咩唔開心事就講出嚟 我地幫你分擔<br />\n希望大家入呢個谷 可以識唔同朋友仔<br />\n係繁忙生活中 係Tg表達大家<br />\n狗公娘娘藍絲退散！<br />\n鴨免會mon住，見到即踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想係個谷見到大家！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44370cc52f80beacba38c6d1b359a83f74f94889","tid":2297841,"uid":128483,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T16:55:56.000Z","msg":"訓之前Up<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee1267eecee2dc1e92f6533270eb239f89f245e","tid":2297841,"uid":128483,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T03:34:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEXW_tW9HVmkzpSkEg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEXW_tW9HVmkzpSkEg&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=b105c2af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEXW_tW9HVmkzpSkEg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等緊你地"},{"pid":"e75f5d2c661c3bbe986302ab796471f47ff433ff","tid":2297841,"uid":128483,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"rep